    "title": "Digital Marketing Manager Vacancy at Firstcry - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Firstcry. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Digital Marketing Manager to strengthen our Mysuru-based team.\n\nAbout Firstcry:\nFirstcry is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Firstcry!",
